{"tid":1923771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動啦手足]]法治已死，已經無路可退 - 3.15 「美國戰線，如箭在弦」網上集會","createTime":"2020-03-13T09:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T11:08:04.000Z","uid":42194,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"550355c8fb2f6f239f60a9ab4aa907289c1319a1","tid":1923771,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"響呢個post 嘅開始之前<br />\n想請大家聽一聽呢首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q5fGK68yNj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq5fGK68yNj8&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=8b8f1c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q5fGK68yNj8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士得到平反未？<br />\n我地未贏呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足俾狗屈打成招<br />\n有手足俾狗打到入院上唔到庭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日依然有好多手足受到清算<br />\n法治已死，我地已經無路可退<br />\n<br />\n大家要加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVOmgk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVOmgk5.jpg&h=ef2941e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.15 「美國戰線，如箭在弦」網上集會 - 關注人權法案首份年檢報告<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年3月15日(日)<br />\n時間：晚上7時至9時<br />\n主辦：民間集會團隊<br />\n協辦：大專學界國際事務代表團前發言人張崑陽、中西區區議員梁晃維<br />\n直播：民間集會團隊Facebook和YouTube<br />\n<br />\n3.15  Online rally &quot;Liberate HK: Advancing the American Front&quot;<br />\n- On the first annual report of HKHRDA<br />\n<br />\nDate: 15th March 2020<br />\nTime: 1900 - 2100<br />\nHost: Hong Kong Civil Assembly Team (HKCAT)<br />\nCo-Organizers: Mr. Sunny CHEUNG, Former Spokesperson of HKIAD ; Mr. Fergus LEUNG, Member of CWDC<br />\nLive: HKCAT Facebook page and YouTube channel<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdas